crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: INDICATOR-OBFUSCATION Gzip encoded HTTP response with no Content-Length or chunked Transfer-Encoding header
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"INDICATOR-OBFUSCATION Gzip encoded HTTP response with no Content-Length or chunked Transfer-Encoding header"; flow:to_client,established; http_header; content:"Content-Encoding: gzip",fast_pattern,nocase; content:!"Content-Length: ",nocase; content:!"Transfer-Encoding: ",nocase; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:http; reference:url,attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1027; reference:url,attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1140; classtype:non-standard-protocol; sid:42017; rev:2; )
alert ( gid:119; sid:228; rev:2; msg:"(http_inspect) server response before client request"; metadata: rule-type preproc; classtype:unknown;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: (http_inspect) HTTP request method is not known to Snort
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert ( gid:119; sid:31; rev:3; msg:"(http_inspect) HTTP request method is not known to Snort"; metadata: policy max-detect-ips drop, rule-type preproc; classtype:unknown;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: SURICATA Applayer Detect protocol only one direction
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert ip any any -> any any (msg:"SURICATA Applayer Detect protocol only one direction"; flow:established; app-layer-event:applayer_detect_protocol_only_one_direction; flowint:applayer.anomaly.count,+,1; classtype:protocol-command-decode; sid:2260002; rev:1;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER Remote non-JavaScript file found in script tag src attribute
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp $EXTERNAL_NET $FILE_DATA_PORTS -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER Remote non-JavaScript file found in script tag src attribute"; flow:to_client,established; file_data; content:"<script"; content:"src=",within 30; isdataat:50,relative; isdataat:!100,relative; content:!"|2E|js",within 50; service:ftp-data,http,imap,pop3; reference:cve,2015-1729; reference:url,technet.microsoft.com/en-us/security/bulletin/MS15-065; classtype:policy-violation; sid:35180; rev:3; )
